{"type": "article", "id": 15528, "title": "小丑杯和大理石", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-25T06:30:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000337tCB37QM5IuvX6gA0.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t法国设计师 Pierre Charpin 在伦敦的 Kreo 画廊里做了小丑杯和大理石搭配的展示。小丑杯一共十件，用简洁几何形状和不同的颜色勾勒出小丑微笑、惊恐或哭泣的不同表情。每一个小丑都有一个红色的陶瓷鼻子，成为杯子的立体的点缀，非常形象。它们共同和下面庄重典雅而原始大理石构成有趣的反差。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142613rGfMZCjAwlYFs7vU.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"778\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142613Mz8rV5FoyeYIsLnJ.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"798\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142614nqJTbYX2F9UZG47j.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"798\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142615UMIbTz5dWmFJcO01.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"798\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142616m6DG8HfcxlCIVa9u.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"662\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}